  - LeadStatus ✅
  - LeadSource ✅
  - Lead (essential fields) ✅
  - Note ✅
- Essential API endpoints ✅
  - GET /api/lead-statuses ✅
  - GET /api/lead-sources ✅
  - GET /api/leads (basic listing) ✅
  - POST /api/leads (creation) ✅
  - GET /api/leads/[id] (detail) ✅

